		<h1 class="pb-2 font-bold text-3xl text-gray-600">Let's talk about GraphQL</h1>
    
      <p class="text-sm italic mb-4">It's a 10 minute read</p>
    
	</div>
  <div class="text-content">
    <p>Historically developing API‚Äôs has been a pain for developers. And the way we develop API‚Äôs needs evolve to keep up with how we consume API‚Äôs across multiple platforms.</p>

<p>Enter GraphQL; a query language developed by Facebook in 2012 and which was later released publicly in 2015. It has been gaining a lot of traction over the last few years, with companies such as GitHub, Shopify, Netflix, and Spotify using it to develop their API‚Äôs.</p>

